{"tid":2201864,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中共威逼利誘推漢語 家長偕兒女匿草原  內蒙校長護學生 辭職自殺","createTime":"2020-09-14T06:38:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-14T07:46:37.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"40f450e80c8fecb6609739dfd221cd3400feffda","tid":2201864,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T06:38:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200914/S74YXXNM75FSNKHUCV7UP5FERU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200914%2FS74YXXNM75FSNKHUCV7UP5FERU%2F&d=L%2FLAiDqbkajbTQHtoaAw8Phh9XvCW3eHRhDz%2B7Q%2FvTo%3D&h=cbe80ebf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200914%2FS74YXXNM75FSNKHUCV7UP5FERU%2F&h=e0ffebd1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200914/S74YXXNM75FSNKHUCV7UP5FERU/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n中共威逼利誘推漢語 家長偕兒女匿草原 <br />\n內蒙校長護學生 辭職自殺<br />\n<br />\n中共近月在內蒙古強推漢語教學，激起蒙人激烈反抗，蒙族人官員幹部亦加入抵制，蒙族家長甚至不讓孩子返校。中共軟硬兼施，派錢利誘學校及學生叫人回校，並以取消學籍作威脅；有家長帶學生到荒涼草原躲避。有指公安部長趙克志月初到內蒙古時曾下令鎮壓，但仍未能平息事件。昨日，內地消息又傳出，內蒙一名中學校長不願取消罷課學生學籍，辭職後自殺身亡，使蒙族人倍添憤怒。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：趕絕內蒙防親俄 京憂腹背受敵<br />\n<br />\n上月底，通遼市、鄂爾多斯市、呼和浩特市等多地爆發示威，。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/WUIp2QD3OvAmPHo3G05YVzQlMJ4=/3323x2215/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/VJD7A3K6CJBMDN4B7AM6O6TWAM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FWUIp2QD3OvAmPHo3G05YVzQlMJ4%3D%2F3323x2215%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FVJD7A3K6CJBMDN4B7AM6O6TWAM.jpg&h=6276389a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■蒙古民眾曾上街抗議內蒙政府封殺蒙語。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n派錢誘回校 威脅取消學籍<br />\n<br />\n赤峰市的共青團翁牛特旗委員會昨日推出「一拖一」的獎勵方式，通知指當地兩間中學及六間小學的在校學生，每讓一位罷課同學回校，即可獲200元人民幣（約226港元）；該委員會又稱，如一個班級的回校率達95%或以上，可獲由該旗的教育局、團委頒發「優秀班集體」證書。<br />\n<br />\n赤峰市的大板鎮則用較為強硬的手段。如當地大板一中在微信發佈緊急通知，。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n在當局不斷要求蒙族學生回校時，不少蒙族牧民開車到草原暫避風頭，詎料官員幹部開車尾隨，直闖牧民住所騷擾。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n二連浩特蒙古族中學校長烏蘭日前因不滿強推漢語政策而辭職，昨日在家自殺身亡。網絡消息指，她拒絕遵從上級指示，。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n另一邊廂，藏語學校今年亦被安排與漢語學校合併，即使藏族父母反對，藏族學生今年開學都要接受漢語教育。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n自由亞洲電台<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/y1rjDuavmdKXllUAP1Lg-BBUjF8=/2104x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/6DAVVO2TNRFLTHU6A34JEGO4DQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fy1rjDuavmdKXllUAP1Lg-BBUjF8%3D%2F2104x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F6DAVVO2TNRFLTHU6A34JEGO4DQ.jpg&h=bbc9a4b9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■內蒙市民聯署要求地方政府用蒙文教學。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/-HIQYn3vVwjiuZaDZ3R43sB8PJc=/2277x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/EJSVWPERJVBENHHYXQNM4KIEYI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F-HIQYn3vVwjiuZaDZ3R43sB8PJc%3D%2F2277x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FEJSVWPERJVBENHHYXQNM4KIEYI.jpg&h=3a410fab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■二連浩特蒙古族中學校長烏蘭（左二），因拒取消罷課生學籍，不敵壓力而自殺。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/jZaho5MPnULAyEco5SpJcgf5Wns=/1029x1024/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/4ZMI4JMAPVA7BA2IE6CK5TGHUU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FjZaho5MPnULAyEco5SpJcgf5Wns%3D%2F1029x1024%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F4ZMI4JMAPVA7BA2IE6CK5TGHUU.jpg&h=c6dc0da3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■內蒙學生與家長走到草原躲避。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/FK47Cnyi4E4zgC_MGgsb7P0ps7M=/475x2197/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/3CS7MZB6YVBIDH5MSU6QKFXB2Q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FFK47Cnyi4E4zgC_MGgsb7P0ps7M%3D%2F475x2197%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F3CS7MZB6YVBIDH5MSU6QKFXB2Q.jpg&h=4d7e397c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6120478898f2bdf6eb932896ea81eea935c3a049","tid":2201864,"uid":11809,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T06:55:01.000Z","msg":"正仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fbdf027278b695b7a86df27f9b5f76dc9268583","tid":2201864,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T06:57:51.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"527dd68bc97c4ff8ee27a38dd02ae09bf7d244ab","tid":2201864,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T07:42:46.000Z","msg":"網傳蒙古小學校長為捍衛母語自殺，孩子們上課都哭了。 | #香港大紀元<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2201933\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2201933</a>"},{"pid":"47b5c60b918d10cef0b2efc424fdad4e2898c6dc","tid":2201864,"uid":214502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T07:43:39.000Z","msg":"支那<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edcd94b3b1394f75937ba91441d2606c6767332c","tid":2201864,"uid":112551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T07:46:35.000Z","msg":"唔怪得中共做得咁絕，內蒙民族心咁強，如果香港無藍屍既話香港都可能唔會溫水煮蛙 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53a1cf891aa8207df22c7eedff5672264d7efa22","tid":2201864,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T07:46:37.000Z","msg":"點解中共一定做親都係壞事 小小好野都冇？"}]}